article_title: Israel launches deadly air strikes in Lebanon
sentence: One  Israeli  soldier  was  killed  and  seven  others  were  wounded  after  their  base  in  Safed  was  hit  by  rockets,  Israeli  media  and  emergency  services  said.

article_title: Israel launches deadly air strikes in Lebanon
sentence: The  soldier  who  died  was  later  identified  as  Staff-Sergeant  Omer  Sarah  Benjo.
